704938f-a.title: Brooklyn: Hicks Street - Amity Street
704938f-a.text:
Hicks Street, west side, south from Pacific to Amity treets.
The clearance next to the corner (left) was occupied by
tenement; and so was the clearance on the extreme left.
P. L. 'uerr  January 10, 1941
